Manager, Finance (T)
What do we do?
Bell Technical Solutions is a wholly owned subsidiary of Bell Canada that specializes in the installation of Bell services, including home phone, Internet and Fibe TV. Together, our 6000+ employees work diligently to provide Canadians with the necessary technology to connect and communicate with their family and friends from across the country and the world.
What is the opportunity?
Reporting to the Senior Manager – Finance, the Manager, Finance will be responsible for providing proactive and quality financial planning and analysis to the Bell Technical Solutions management team as well as working with the Finance Team to deliver month-end processes and related reports.
What will you do?
Prepare monthly, quarterly, and annual divisional budgets and deliver quality variance analysis and customer service to the divisional Director;
